    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="HashSet与HashMap"><a href="#HashSet与HashMap" class="headerlink" title="HashSet与HashMap"></a>HashSet与HashMap</h2><p>HashSet<strong>底层</strong>是什么？</p><p>HashMap</p><p>key value </p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">boolean</span> <span class="title">add</span><span class="params">(E e)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> map.put(e, PRESENT)==<span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>HashSet<strong>也是线程不安全的</strong>。</p><p><img src="/img/image-20191226150357090.png" alt="image-20191226150357090"></p><p>ArrayList HashSet HashMap 都是线程不安全的 都会报并发修改异常</p><p>Hash Map的解决同样是concurrentHashMap</p><h2 id="八锁问题："><a href="#八锁问题：" class="headerlink" title="八锁问题："></a>八锁问题：</h2><p><img src="/img/image-20191226152040654.png" alt="image-20191226152040654"></p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">synchronized</span> 锁的是对象</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/image-20191226153759978.png" alt="image-20191226153759978"></p>]]></content>
    
